              l2 = c("2D1","2E3", "2E5", "2E7", "2E6", "2E8", "2E1", "2E2", "2E4","2A1", "2A3", "2A2","2B2", "2B6", "2B1", "2B5", "2B4", "2B7", "2B8", "2B9", "2B3","2C1", "2C2"),
             l3 = c("3A1", "3A2","3B1", "3B2a", "3B2b", "3B3", "3C1", "3C2", "3C3", "3E1", "3D1","3F1", "3F2", "3F3", "3G1"),
             l4 = c("4A1","4A2", "4A3", "4A4","4B1", "4B10", "4B5", "4B6", "4B7", "4B8", "4B4", "4B2", "4B3","4C4", "4C3", "4C1", "4C2", "4C12", "4C15", "4C14", "4C7", "4C16", "4C17", "4C8","4C5", "4C6", "4C11", "4C9", "4C10"),
             l5 = c("45A1", "45A2","45B1", "45F1","45C1", "45C2","45D1","45E1","45G1", "45G2", "45G3", "45G4"),

             l12 = c("10A2", "10A1"),
             l13 = c("8A2", "8A1"))
all_akrs_plot <- groupOTU(all_akrs, cls0)
all_akrs_plot <- ggtree(all_akrs_plot, layout = "circular", branch.length = "none", aes(color=group)) +
  scale_color_manual(values=c(rainbow_hcl(14))) + theme(legend.position="none") + geom_nodepoint() + geom_tiplab()
all_akrs_plot
